  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Financial relief to victims",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy and Power Minister Kanchana Wijesekara said through a Twitter post that the need for kerosene price revision has been mandatory for many years.",
        "He also mentioned that the government has decided to provide relief to low income families, fisheries and horticulture sectors dependent on kerosene.",
        "He said the government has proposed to provide direct cash relief to the above families and sectors with prices commensurate with the expenses.",
        "He pointed out that the sale of kerosene at subsidized prices was also a major reason for the collapse of the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation.",
        "A liter of kerosene has been hiked by Rs 253 to Rs 340 with effect from midnight on Sunday (21), which was Rs 87."
      ],
